  <h3>URL encoding for tags</h3>

  <p>Tags with spaces or special characters need URL encoding:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Tag</th>
        <th>URL</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>digital-modes</code></td>
        <td><code>/tags/digital-modes</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>rare DXCC</code></td>
        <td><code>/tags/rare%20DXCC</code></td>
